{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":964,"text":"When, in 1960, still a student,"},{"time":3734,"text":"I got a traveling fellowship"},{"time":6159,"text":"to study housing in North America."},{"time":9220,"text":"We traveled the country."},{"time":11504,"text":"We saw public housing high-rise buildings"},{"time":14609,"text":"in all major cities:"},{"time":16950,"text":"New York, Philadelphia."},{"time":19030,"text":"Those who have no choice lived there."},{"time":21999,"text":"And then we traveled from suburb to suburb,"},{"time":24294,"text":"and I came back thinking,"},{"time":26342,"text":"we've got to reinvent the apartment building."},{"time":28996,"text":"There has to be another way of doing this."},{"time":31675,"text":"We can't sustain suburbs,"},{"time":33710,"text":"so let's design a building"},{"time":36275,"text":"which gives the qualities of a house"},{"time":39518,"text":"to each unit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40689,"text":"Habitat would be all about gardens,"},{"time":44850,"text":"contact with nature,"},{"time":46755,"text":"streets instead of corridors."},{"time":48939,"text":"We prefabricated it so we would achieve economy,"},{"time":52737,"text":"and there it is almost 50 years later."},{"time":57980,"text":"It's a very desirable place to live in."},{"time":61351,"text":"It's now a heritage building,"},{"time":63810,"text":"but it did not proliferate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67413,"text":"In 1973, I made my first trip to China."},{"time":72117,"text":"It was the Cultural Revolution."},{"time":76383,"text":"We traveled the country,"},{"time":78531,"text":"met with architects and planners."},{"time":81760,"text":"This is Beijing then,"},{"time":83976,"text":"not a single high rise building"},{"time":86848,"text":"in Beijing or Shanghai."},{"time":89132,"text":"Shenzhen didn't even exist as a city."},{"time":92990,"text":"There were hardly any cars."},{"time":96269,"text":"Thirty years later,"},{"time":98920,"text":"this is Beijing today."},{"time":101915,"text":"This is Hong Kong."},{"time":103628,"text":"If you're wealthy, you live there,"},{"time":106128,"text":"if you're poor, you live there,"},{"time":108548,"text":"but high density it is, and it's not just Asia."},{"time":111214,"text":"SÃ£o Paulo, you can travel"},{"time":113171,"text":"in a helicopter 45 minutes"},{"time":115695,"text":"seeing those high-rise buildings consume"},{"time":117705,"text":"the 19th-century low-rise environment."},{"time":120341,"text":"And with it, comes congestion,"},{"time":122652,"text":"and we lose mobility, and so on and so forth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126674,"text":"So a few years ago, we decided to go back"},{"time":129224,"text":"and rethink Habitat."},{"time":131138,"text":"Could we make it more affordable?"},{"time":133827,"text":"Could we actually achieve this quality of life"},{"time":136890,"text":"in the densities that are prevailing today?"},{"time":141297,"text":"And we realized, it's basically about light,"},{"time":144160,"text":"it's about sun, it's about nature,"},{"time":147222,"text":"it's about fractalization."},{"time":149402,"text":"Can we open up the surface of the building"},{"time":152631,"text":"so that it has more contact with the exterior?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":155499,"text":"We came up with a number of models:"},{"time":157738,"text":"economy models, cheaper to build and more compact;"},{"time":161574,"text":"membranes of housing"},{"time":163621,"text":"where people could design their own house"},{"time":165980,"text":"and create their own gardens."},{"time":168087,"text":"And then we decided to take New York as a test case,"},{"time":171968,"text":"and we looked at Lower Manhattan."},{"time":174015,"text":"And we mapped all the building area in Manhattan."},{"time":177840,"text":"On the left is Manhattan today:"},{"time":181215,"text":"blue for housing, red for office buildings, retail."},{"time":185602,"text":"On the right, we reconfigured it:"},{"time":188201,"text":"the office buildings form the base,"},{"time":190518,"text":"and then rising 75 stories above,"},{"time":193781,"text":"are apartments."},{"time":195160,"text":"There's a street in the air on the 25th level,"},{"time":198136,"text":"a community street."},{"time":200150,"text":"It's permeable."},{"time":201759,"text":"There are gardens and open spaces"},{"time":203712,"text":"for the community,"},{"time":205156,"text":"almost every unit with its own private garden,"},{"time":208365,"text":"and community space all around."},{"time":211027,"text":"And most important, permeable, open."},{"time":214187,"text":"It does not form a wall or an obstruction in the city,"},{"time":217584,"text":"and light permeates everywhere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220419,"text":"And in the last two or three years,"},{"time":222076,"text":"we've actually been, for the first time,"},{"time":224648,"text":"realizing the quality of life of Habitat"},{"time":228361,"text":"in real-life projects across Asia."},{"time":232068,"text":"This in Qinhuangdao in China:"},{"time":235302,"text":"middle-income housing, where there is a bylaw"},{"time":237880,"text":"that every apartment must receive"},{"time":240587,"text":"three hours of sunlight."},{"time":243343,"text":"That's measured in the winter solstice."},{"time":246233,"text":"And under construction in Singapore,"},{"time":249660,"text":"again middle-income housing, gardens,"},{"time":252882,"text":"community streets and parks and so on and so forth."},{"time":256748,"text":"And Colombo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":259198,"text":"And I want to touch on one more issue,"},{"time":261414,"text":"which is the design of the public realm."},{"time":265099,"text":"A hundred years after we've begun building"},{"time":268693,"text":"with tall buildings,"},{"time":270425,"text":"we are yet to understand"},{"time":272765,"text":"how the tall high-rise building"},{"time":275690,"text":"becomes a building block in making a city,"},{"time":278525,"text":"in creating the public realm."},{"time":281348,"text":"In Singapore, we had an opportunity:"},{"time":283767,"text":"10 million square feet, extremely high density."},{"time":286990,"text":"Taking the concept of outdoor and indoor,"},{"time":291112,"text":"promenades and parks integrated"},{"time":293363,"text":"with intense urban life."},{"time":295545,"text":"So they are outdoor spaces and indoor spaces,"},{"time":299133,"text":"and you move from one to the other,"},{"time":301110,"text":"and there is contact with nature,"},{"time":303217,"text":"and most relevantly, at every level of the structure,"},{"time":307188,"text":"public gardens and open space:"},{"time":309877,"text":"on the roof of the podium,"},{"time":311643,"text":"climbing up the towers,"},{"time":313442,"text":"and finally on the roof, the sky park,"},{"time":317380,"text":"two and a half acres, jogging paths, restaurants,"},{"time":320754,"text":"and the world's longest swimming pool."},{"time":326109,"text":"And that's all I can tell you in five minutes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":328865,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330733,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}